channel.title: Make me LOL
channel.description:
It's been ages since i've LOl'd for REAL. You know when your friends say a joke that sucks, and you really don['t care much but you laugh anyways? Yeah that isnt LOl'ing. i actually wanna LOL. Btw:
Last time I lol'd was when i typed this, then reread it:
A kid was in general saying "hi" and everybody else said "welcome" i said this...
Little tuptup came to town, prancing like a pony. Popped a cap in his ass and called pwnage-roni!
(tuptup was his name)
lol i laughed
